The girlfriend of a British man who bled to death in Thailand after injuring himself kicking a mirror in the bar where she works has denied having anything to do with the incident .
Iain Mackay , 40 , is believed to have argued with Nilobon Patty in a separate venue in Hua Hin , a resort .
Ms Patty , 35 , has been accused of ` indirectly causing his death ' but claims she has done nothing wrong .